flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 29: Vendor Performance Score Computation and Tiering Flow

  DeliveryEvent[Order delivery event]
  WeeklyRefresh[Weekly full refresh job]
  Start[Start VPS computation]

  Collect[Collect component metrics\nFulfillment Rate\nAvg Rating\nResponse-to-Ship Time\nDelivery Accuracy\nDispute Rate]
  MetricsCheck{All component metrics available?}
  Fallback[Use prior metric snapshot for missing fields\nMark score as confidence-reduced]

  Weighting[Weighted score model\n35% Fulfillment\n25% Rating\n15% Response-to-Ship\n15% Delivery Accuracy\n10% Dispute Rate]
  Score[Compute VPS 0-100]
  TierDecision{Assign tier}

  Platinum[Platinum 85+]
  Gold[Gold 70-84]
  Silver[Silver 50-69]
  Watch[Watch <50]

  PlatinumAction[Promotion + potential commission benefits]
  GoldAction[Standard operations]
  SilverAction[Warning notices + coaching prompts]
  WatchAction[Suspension risk workflow]

  Output[Return VPS payload\nscore, tier, component breakdown, trend]

  DeliveryEvent --> Start
  WeeklyRefresh --> Start

  Start --> Collect --> MetricsCheck
  MetricsCheck -- Yes --> Weighting
  MetricsCheck -- No --> Fallback --> Weighting

  Weighting --> Score --> TierDecision

  TierDecision -- Platinum --> Platinum --> PlatinumAction --> Output
  TierDecision -- Gold --> Gold --> GoldAction --> Output
  TierDecision -- Silver --> Silver --> SilverAction --> Output
  TierDecision -- Watch --> Watch --> WatchAction --> Output
